♪Time will speak your truth aloud♪

17
00:01:24,690 --> 00:01:26,848
♪No time gap between tomorrow and I♪

18
00:01:26,848 --> 00:01:29,010
♪Tears are blossoming♪

19
00:01:29,010 --> 00:01:31,110
♪The path of hope never divides♪

20
00:01:31,110 --> 00:01:33,280
♪Waiting for sunlight's embrace♪

21
00:01:36,570 --> 00:01:38,240
♪Just right now♪

22
00:01:38,670 --> 00:01:40,030
♪Take the field immediately♪

23
00:01:40,798 --> 00:01:44,015
=All Rise=

24
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:47,592
=Episode 21=

25
00:01:48,808 --> 00:01:49,800
(Talent Hunt Program Day 67)

26
00:01:50,024 --> 00:01:52,040
(Guo Xiaoyu 3, Yan Fei 2)

27
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:53,864
(Ren Jiatong 1, Jiang Chen 1)

28
00:01:55,048 --> 00:01:55,688
Have you heard?

29
00:01:56,067 --> 00:01:57,787
The client Ms. Bai just met with

30
00:01:57,986 --> 00:01:59,227
is her ex-boyfriend.

31
00:01:59,707 --> 00:02:01,186
And this guy came to see Ms. Bai

32
00:02:01,386 --> 00:02:02,986
to help his current girlfriend.

33
00:02:03,707 --> 00:02:05,067
I'm so furious!

34
00:02:05,307 --> 00:02:06,986
What's wrong with these men?

35
00:02:07,027 --> 00:02:08,186
Are they all heartless?

36
00:02:10,547 --> 00:02:12,746
Maybe you should add a prerequisite

37
00:02:13,027 --> 00:02:14,387
to your conclusion.

38
00:02:14,666 --> 00:02:15,786
Let's be more rigorous.

39
00:02:15,827 --> 00:02:16,946
Don't target the innocent.

40
00:02:23,346 --> 00:02:24,488
I'm being quite rigorous.

41
00:02:27,666 --> 00:02:28,987
I didn't misjudge any bad man.

42
00:02:32,107 --> 00:02:33,626
I'm just so mad.

43
00:02:33,987 --> 00:02:36,186
I don't think
Ms. Bai will take this case.

44
00:02:36,267 --> 00:02:38,027
It's generous
that she didn't kick him out.

45
00:02:38,226 --> 00:02:40,587
But my gut feeling is
Ms. Bai will take the case.

46
00:02:41,427 --> 00:02:42,587
I also think so.

47
00:02:43,346 --> 00:02:45,346
Ms. Bai doesn't
let emotions affect her work.

48
00:02:45,827 --> 00:02:47,666
This isn't about emotions.

49
00:02:47,666 --> 00:02:48,987
It's about basic self-respect.

50
00:02:49,346 --> 00:02:49,946
Think about it.

51
00:02:50,107 --> 00:02:52,147
Since her divorce,

52
00:02:52,267 --> 00:02:54,466
he's the only boyfriend
Ms. Bai has ever acknowledged.

53
00:02:54,466 --> 00:02:56,147
She almost committed to him.

54
00:02:56,346 --> 00:02:57,387
I don't know exactly why

55
00:02:57,387 --> 00:02:58,307
they broke up later,

56
00:02:58,506 --> 00:03:00,987
but I'd guess that in Ms. Bai's heart,

57
00:03:01,186 --> 00:03:03,107
he probably meant more than my idol.

58
00:03:04,107 --> 00:03:06,626
I bet you 100 yuan. She won't take it.

59
00:03:14,027 --> 00:03:16,506
What are you discussing?
Not at your desk

60
00:03:16,506 --> 00:03:17,387
and already slacking?

61
00:03:18,267 --> 00:03:19,346
Let me say something here.

62
00:03:20,226 --> 00:03:22,027
Ms. Bai has taken on the bribery case

63
00:03:22,027 --> 00:03:23,746
involving Xia Jun at Mr. Gao's request.

64
00:03:24,906 --> 00:03:25,626
I'll send you

65
00:03:25,786 --> 00:03:27,267
case files and assignments shortly.

66
00:03:27,466 --> 00:03:29,107
Get familiar with the case immediately.

67
00:03:29,147 --> 00:03:30,027
Finish it promptly.

68
00:03:30,466 --> 00:03:31,186
But

69
00:03:31,186 --> 00:03:32,707
their connections are tangled,

70
00:03:32,987 --> 00:03:33,626
being coworkers,

71
00:03:33,626 --> 00:03:34,666
client and contractor,

72
00:03:34,867 --> 00:03:36,267
and exes. It's complicated.

73
00:03:36,267 --> 00:03:36,906
Enough.

74
00:03:38,066 --> 00:03:38,666
Ms. Guo,

75
00:03:39,147 --> 00:03:40,147
we're a Red Circle Firm,

76
00:03:40,186 --> 00:03:41,147
not a matchmaker.

77
00:03:41,906 --> 00:03:43,387
Stop analyzing relationships.

78
00:03:44,307 --> 00:03:44,666
Okay.

79
00:03:45,147 --> 00:03:45,946
Keep work as work

80
00:03:46,267 --> 00:03:46,946
and love as love.

81
00:03:47,506 --> 00:03:48,267
Don't mix the two.

82
00:03:49,506 --> 00:03:51,626
Guo Xiaoyu, Ren Jiatong,
go find Ms. Tian.

83
00:03:52,147 --> 00:03:53,267
Meet the client with her

84
00:03:53,387 --> 00:03:54,506
and get more case details.

85
00:03:55,147 --> 00:03:57,267
Jiang Chen, Yan Fei,
send me the key points

86
00:03:57,267 --> 00:03:58,792
from Xia Jun's internal report soon.

87
00:04:05,346 --> 00:04:07,466
Mr. Zhou, she might get
some urgent work to do.

88
00:04:10,626 --> 00:04:11,387
Get back to work.

89
00:04:13,626 --> 00:04:14,312
Give me 100 yuan.

90
00:04:14,547 --> 00:04:14,867
Shut up.

91
00:04:38,986 --> 00:04:39,426
Yan Fei,

92
00:04:40,466 --> 00:04:42,507
no rush on your report.
Tomorrow is fine.

93
00:04:44,187 --> 00:04:44,507
Okay.

94
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:10,312
(When are you coming back?)

95
00:06:11,466 --> 00:06:12,666
Here. Have some water.

96
00:06:13,906 --> 00:06:15,786
Your girlfriend didn't
come train with you?

97
00:06:16,187 --> 00:06:17,106
Not my girlfriend.

98
00:06:17,707 --> 00:06:18,426
We are colleagues.

99
00:06:33,106 --> 00:06:35,106
I just met Xia Jun with Guo Xiaoyu.

100
00:06:35,426 --> 00:06:37,346
She admitted recommending introduction

101
00:06:37,346 --> 00:06:39,666
of the outsourcing software company
at their request,

102
00:06:39,666 --> 00:06:40,587
but denied bribery.

103
00:06:40,906 --> 00:06:41,866
But they insisted

104
00:06:41,866 --> 00:06:43,627
they gave her
two million cash personally,

105
00:06:43,827 --> 00:06:45,306
with times, locations, and witnesses.

106
00:06:45,666 --> 00:06:47,306
Their internal investigation report

107
00:06:47,387 --> 00:06:49,747
listed several locations where they met,

108
00:06:50,067 --> 00:06:51,986
including a seafood restaurant
and a pub.

109
00:06:52,267 --> 00:06:54,507
But Xia Jun claimed she has
severe seafood allergy.

110
00:06:54,587 --> 00:06:56,507
She'd never meet
at a seafood restaurant.

111
00:06:56,906 --> 00:06:58,627
So they're probably lying.

112
00:06:59,387 --> 00:06:59,986
I'm on it.

113
00:07:00,747 --> 00:07:02,666
I'll visit

114
00:07:02,747 --> 00:07:03,627
all those places

115
00:07:03,627 --> 00:07:05,587
and see if I'd have any chance

116
00:07:05,587 --> 00:07:06,546
to check footage.

117
00:07:07,106 --> 00:07:08,546
I'll update you if I find anything.

118
00:07:09,666 --> 00:07:10,027
Okay.

119
00:07:14,306 --> 00:07:15,080
Have you eaten?

120
00:07:16,786 --> 00:07:17,587
Xiaoyu is cooking.

121
00:07:18,827 --> 00:07:19,587
I'm also hungry.

122
00:07:23,546 --> 00:07:28,226
It depends on your performance.
If you find solid evidence,

123
00:07:28,707 --> 00:07:30,440
we'll save you a bite
for a midnight snack.

124
00:07:32,747 --> 00:07:34,986
What if I can't find anything?

125
00:07:37,627 --> 00:07:38,866
Then I'll be merciful

126
00:07:39,346 --> 00:07:40,387
and grab some with you.

127
00:07:42,226 --> 00:07:42,546
Deal.

128
00:07:43,466 --> 00:07:44,584
Jiatong, noodles are ready.

129
00:07:46,466 --> 00:07:47,027
Talk later.

130
00:07:49,627 --> 00:07:50,147
Who is it?

131
00:07:53,147 --> 00:07:53,747
Jiang Chen.

132
00:07:54,507 --> 00:07:55,707
I've updated them

133
00:07:55,707 --> 00:07:56,947
with today's information.

134
00:07:56,947 --> 00:07:57,906
Yan Fei hasn't replied.

135
00:07:57,906 --> 00:07:59,187
Jiang Chen called me back.

136
00:08:03,587 --> 00:08:04,707
He didn't say anything else?

137
00:08:07,627 --> 00:08:08,106
No.

138
00:08:16,507 --> 00:08:16,906
Jiatong,

139
00:08:19,147 --> 00:08:20,507
we're best friends.

140
00:08:21,866 --> 00:08:23,786
There's something I have to tell you.

141
00:08:26,187 --> 00:08:26,947
What is it?

142
00:08:26,947 --> 00:08:27,747
So mysterious.

143
00:08:31,906 --> 00:08:32,546
I think

144
00:08:33,227 --> 00:08:35,946
Yan Fei and Jiang Chen have
something going on.

145
00:08:40,147 --> 00:08:41,267
What could be going on?

146
00:08:41,467 --> 00:08:42,826
What else could it possibly be?

147
00:08:42,826 --> 00:08:44,186
Are you an idiot? Think about it.

148
00:08:44,627 --> 00:08:46,027
How we obsess over couples?

149
00:08:46,467 --> 00:08:48,666
We examine every little detail
with a magnifying glass.

150
00:08:48,747 --> 00:08:50,467
At the slightest hint,

151
00:08:50,546 --> 00:08:52,027
we'll imagine an entire love story.

152
00:08:52,507 --> 00:08:53,027
Listen.

153
00:08:53,306 --> 00:08:53,747
Lately,

154
00:08:54,267 --> 00:08:55,546
whenever I post on Moments,

155
00:08:55,546 --> 00:08:56,586
Jiang Chen likes it.

156
00:08:56,786 --> 00:08:58,066
He never liked my posts before.

157
00:08:58,867 --> 00:08:59,586
Do you know why?

158
00:09:00,306 --> 00:09:00,946
Why?

159
00:09:02,387 --> 00:09:02,987
I bet

160
00:09:04,107 --> 00:09:06,027
it's because I'm close friends
with Yan Fei.

161
00:09:07,867 --> 00:09:09,387
This is all way too suspicious.

162
00:09:10,387 --> 00:09:12,347
Last time, I posted our group photo.

163
00:09:12,586 --> 00:09:13,507
He liked it again,

164
00:09:14,347 --> 00:09:16,467
just because Yan Fei was standing
in the middle.

165
00:09:19,507 --> 00:09:21,107
I didn't want to tell you any of this.

166
00:09:22,306 --> 00:09:22,946
I'm just afraid

167
00:09:23,747 --> 00:09:24,786
you would get hurt.

168
00:09:26,306 --> 00:09:27,906
How could I possibly get hurt?

169
00:09:30,826 --> 00:09:32,586
Alright. Good that you're
taking this well.

170
00:09:34,066 --> 00:09:34,867
Don't blame Yan Fei.

171
00:09:35,186 --> 00:09:36,467
Blame that fool Jiang Chen.

172
00:09:37,147 --> 00:09:37,666
Listen.

173
00:09:38,347 --> 00:09:40,267
Guys can change their feelings
in an instant.

174
00:09:40,747 --> 00:09:41,747
You think you are close,

175
00:09:41,826 --> 00:09:42,987
yet suddenly, he changes.

176
00:09:45,186 --> 00:09:45,946
Several days ago,

177
00:09:46,107 --> 00:09:47,786
I saw an image on Yiaiwan's

178
00:09:47,786 --> 00:09:48,586
beta testing site.

179
00:09:49,387 --> 00:09:50,627
Though anonymously posted,

180
00:09:50,627 --> 00:09:51,906
it must be Zhu Zhisheng's work.

181
00:09:53,426 --> 00:09:54,306
Look at this username.

182
00:09:54,867 --> 00:09:55,867
Rain1016.

183
00:09:56,867 --> 00:09:57,666
That's my birthday.

184
00:09:59,867 --> 00:10:01,107
When he made this image,

185
00:10:02,066 --> 00:10:04,107
he must have been daydreaming
about our future.

186
00:10:07,706 --> 00:10:08,387
Xiaoyu,

187
00:10:09,027 --> 00:10:11,066
you haven't moved on from Zhu Zhisheng?

188
00:10:15,227 --> 00:10:16,186
Honestly, I don't know.

189
00:10:17,906 --> 00:10:19,267
Since I returned from Hangzhou,

190
00:10:19,507 --> 00:10:20,666
I keep telling myself daily

191
00:10:21,387 --> 00:10:22,586
that I must let it go.

192
00:10:23,387 --> 00:10:24,666
He's just some guy.

193
00:10:24,666 --> 00:10:25,946
Just four years of relationship.

194
00:10:26,306 --> 00:10:27,867
No big deal, right?

195
00:10:28,546 --> 00:10:30,306
I don't care at all.

196
00:10:30,306 --> 00:10:31,747
I'll totally forget it.

197
00:10:33,546 --> 00:10:34,627
But sometimes,

198
00:10:35,347 --> 00:10:36,306
with just a random song,

199
00:10:37,227 --> 00:10:38,147
a familiar scent,

200
00:10:39,107 --> 00:10:40,306
or even certain clothes,

201
00:10:41,227 --> 00:10:42,107
just by seeing it,

202
00:10:42,107 --> 00:10:44,027
my heart hurts badly like it's been

203
00:10:44,027 --> 00:10:44,867
punctured.

204
00:10:46,107 --> 00:10:48,066
But when I saw that image recently,

205
00:10:48,627 --> 00:10:49,706
I suddenly realized

206
00:10:51,786 --> 00:10:54,747
maybe dating is just like
playing video games.

207
00:10:55,467 --> 00:10:56,627
Sometimes you play for hours,

208
00:10:57,507 --> 00:10:58,666
but forget to save progress.

209
00:10:59,306 --> 00:11:01,066
All that hard-earned gear disappears.

210
00:11:02,027 --> 00:11:02,987
Or even worse,

211
00:11:03,186 --> 00:11:04,107
you lose your account.

212
00:11:05,387 --> 00:11:05,786
Tell me.

213
00:11:06,627 --> 00:11:07,387
In cases like that,

214
00:11:08,306 --> 00:11:09,586
does that make it all pointless?

215
00:11:13,306 --> 00:11:14,306
Definitely not.

216
00:11:15,426 --> 00:11:17,627
Because I truly experienced

217
00:11:17,627 --> 00:11:19,387
the highs and lows during gameplay.

218
00:11:19,946 --> 00:11:20,786
Those feelings

219
00:11:21,227 --> 00:11:22,906
aren't tied to anyone else.

220
00:11:23,227 --> 00:11:24,426
They belong to me alone.

221
00:11:26,586 --> 00:11:27,627
I just want to tell you.

222
00:11:28,147 --> 00:11:28,507
Jiatong,

223
00:11:29,906 --> 00:11:30,906
whatever we go through,

224
00:11:32,066 --> 00:11:33,586
let's never lose faith in love.

225
00:11:37,747 --> 00:11:39,627
Xiaoyu, you're amazing.

226
00:11:40,426 --> 00:11:40,906
Jiatong,

227
00:11:41,627 --> 00:11:43,627
this is the first time
you hugged me first.

228
00:11:53,147 --> 00:11:54,186
If you're feeling down,

229
00:11:54,747 --> 00:11:55,227
it's okay.

230
00:11:55,786 --> 00:11:57,426
Talk to me. I understand.

231
00:12:02,786 --> 00:12:03,147
Okay.

232
00:12:09,867 --> 00:12:11,066
Earlier, Guo Xiaoyu was

233
00:12:11,066 --> 00:12:12,747
having serious analysis.

234
00:12:13,027 --> 00:12:13,826
I'm torn

235
00:12:14,066 --> 00:12:16,546
about whether to tell her or not.

236
00:12:17,627 --> 00:12:18,987
I'm also afraid that someday

237
00:12:18,987 --> 00:12:20,227
she'll find out and be mad.

238
00:12:21,227 --> 00:12:21,627
Oh, no!

239
00:12:22,426 --> 00:12:24,426
I think I missed the best time
to confess.

240
00:12:25,027 --> 00:12:25,747
So what now?

241
00:12:25,946 --> 00:12:28,066
How about going for leniency now?

242
00:12:28,867 --> 00:12:29,987
Well, there's another way.

243
00:12:30,706 --> 00:12:31,227
What is it?

244
00:12:32,867 --> 00:12:34,227
We can just stop all contact.

245
00:12:37,387 --> 00:12:40,107
Ren Jiatong, you...
Good thing you're not a judge.

246
00:12:40,107 --> 00:12:41,906
You'd cause so many
wrongful convictions.

247
00:12:42,387 --> 00:12:43,426
I can't even imagine.

248
00:12:43,786 --> 00:12:44,706
What did I do?

249
00:12:44,706 --> 00:12:46,227
You're sacrificing me.

250
00:12:46,586 --> 00:12:47,306
I won't accept it.

251
00:12:47,387 --> 00:12:48,306
I'm innocent.

252
00:12:48,627 --> 00:12:49,627
I want to appeal.

253
00:12:50,627 --> 00:12:51,586
Alright, alright.

254
00:12:51,706 --> 00:12:53,267
I restore your innocence.

255
00:12:54,867 --> 00:12:55,706
That's more like it.

256
00:12:57,586 --> 00:12:59,867
Should we do something for Mr. Zhou

257
00:13:00,507 --> 00:13:01,107
and Yan Fei?

258
00:13:01,987 --> 00:13:03,147
Since you brought it up,

259
00:13:03,147 --> 00:13:04,387
you must have a plan.

260
00:13:04,627 --> 00:13:05,227
Tell me.

261
00:13:05,987 --> 00:13:06,747
I have no plan.

262
00:13:07,107 --> 00:13:08,826
How could I have a plan
for their romance?

263
00:13:09,706 --> 00:13:11,107
But I do have invited Mr. Zhou

264
00:13:11,107 --> 00:13:12,027
to investigate later.

265
00:13:12,666 --> 00:13:14,107
I'll see how he's doing then.

266
00:13:14,507 --> 00:13:16,347
If he's completely heartless,

267
00:13:16,347 --> 00:13:17,586
let's just drop it.

268
00:13:18,347 --> 00:13:19,666
Yan Fei is so proud.

269
00:13:19,706 --> 00:13:21,384
She'd feel bad
if we kept bringing it up.

270
00:13:21,747 --> 00:13:22,826
You sure know Yan Fei well.

271
00:13:27,546 --> 00:13:28,906
Who spilled the vinegar?

272
00:13:29,507 --> 00:13:30,627
Smells jealous in here!

273
00:13:32,627 --> 00:13:33,306
Just go!

274
00:13:33,507 --> 00:13:33,987
And then?

275
00:13:34,507 --> 00:13:35,227
Come right back.

276
00:13:37,147 --> 00:13:37,507
Got it!

277
00:13:51,946 --> 00:13:52,546
Just off work?

278
00:13:53,747 --> 00:13:54,107
Mr. Song,

279
00:13:54,267 --> 00:13:55,147
working this late too?

280
00:13:56,987 --> 00:13:58,027
Are you settling back in

281
00:13:58,387 --> 00:13:58,906
with Ms. Bai?

