00:25:47,507 --> 00:25:49,066
Just like we work on a case.

568
00:25:49,586 --> 00:25:50,346
You might think

569
00:25:50,667 --> 00:25:50,987
you'll

570
00:25:50,987 --> 00:25:52,546
lose for sure,

571
00:25:52,907 --> 00:25:54,907
but you still go all out.

572
00:25:56,826 --> 00:25:58,467
Shouldn't love get the same effort?

573
00:26:01,066 --> 00:26:02,826
Mr. Song didn't say it outright,

574
00:26:02,826 --> 00:26:04,667
but I sense he regrets it.

575
00:26:05,386 --> 00:26:07,267
We can't repeat
the older generation's mistakes,

576
00:26:07,747 --> 00:26:08,786
never communicating,

577
00:26:08,786 --> 00:26:09,987
bottling everything up,

578
00:26:10,306 --> 00:26:11,146
assuming others

579
00:26:11,146 --> 00:26:13,066
will magically

580
00:26:13,066 --> 00:26:14,306
understand them,

581
00:26:14,306 --> 00:26:15,227
and missing everything.

582
00:26:20,507 --> 00:26:21,947
I called you out tonight

583
00:26:22,586 --> 00:26:24,546
because I thought hard on the way back.

584
00:26:24,947 --> 00:26:25,507
I believe

585
00:26:26,747 --> 00:26:28,747
if I leave Jun An
and don't go back to Chongqing,

586
00:26:29,507 --> 00:26:30,786
I have other options.

587
00:26:31,427 --> 00:26:32,306
What do you mean?

588
00:26:36,106 --> 00:26:38,306
I'm considering dropping out
of the Talent Hunt Program.

589
00:26:40,187 --> 00:26:40,866
I think you might

590
00:26:40,866 --> 00:26:41,826
need this offer more.

591
00:26:44,707 --> 00:26:45,306
Jiang Chen,

592
00:26:45,947 --> 00:26:47,146
are you pitying me?

593
00:26:48,826 --> 00:26:49,707
You think I can't

594
00:26:49,707 --> 00:26:50,267
earn it myself

595
00:26:50,267 --> 00:26:51,146
unless you step aside?

596
00:26:51,786 --> 00:26:53,427
No! I just thought

597
00:26:53,947 --> 00:26:55,346
this might be better for us.

598
00:26:55,947 --> 00:26:56,826
Don't get mad.

599
00:26:57,146 --> 00:26:57,947
I'm not mad.

600
00:26:58,826 --> 00:27:00,346
Leave if you want.

601
00:27:00,826 --> 00:27:02,227
But if you're doing this for me,

602
00:27:02,626 --> 00:27:03,306
I won't take it.

603
00:27:03,907 --> 00:27:05,066
Don't misunderstand.

604
00:27:05,667 --> 00:27:07,346
I haven't decided anything yet.

605
00:27:07,346 --> 00:27:08,306
And I never said

606
00:27:08,907 --> 00:27:10,386
I'm only doing this for you.

607
00:27:10,987 --> 00:27:12,346
I'm just discussing it with you.

608
00:27:12,747 --> 00:27:14,747
Don't normal couples
discuss things together?

609
00:27:15,267 --> 00:27:17,386
First, we're not dating.

610
00:27:18,626 --> 00:27:20,467
At most, we kissed once.

611
00:27:20,546 --> 00:27:22,786
Whether you call it impulse
due to being drunk

612
00:27:22,947 --> 00:27:24,947
or being stressful and lonely,

613
00:27:25,306 --> 00:27:26,187
that's up to you.

614
00:27:26,747 --> 00:27:28,546
Besides, I don't need you
to give it to me.

615
00:27:29,227 --> 00:27:30,626
Even if you go all out,

616
00:27:31,146 --> 00:27:32,488
you still might not defeat me.

617
00:27:33,586 --> 00:27:34,586
What are you saying?

618
00:27:34,667 --> 00:27:36,066
What do you mean we are not dating?

619
00:27:37,346 --> 00:27:38,306
I'm not targeting you.

620
00:27:38,947 --> 00:27:40,346
I'm just not interested in love.

621
00:27:42,267 --> 00:27:44,667
Especially if it means
you are sacrificing for me.

622
00:27:45,747 --> 00:27:46,546
I can't bear that.

623
00:27:48,306 --> 00:27:50,146
Ren Jiatong, what are you so afraid of?

624
00:27:50,826 --> 00:27:53,346
What... What can't you face?

625
00:27:53,507 --> 00:27:54,546
Why are you so

626
00:27:55,227 --> 00:27:57,146
afraid to admit your own feelings?

627
00:27:57,146 --> 00:27:58,907
You act cold,

628
00:27:59,146 --> 00:28:00,546
giving off a standoffish vibe.

629
00:28:01,146 --> 00:28:02,187
Do you think that's cool?

630
00:28:02,187 --> 00:28:03,227
Or will it protect you?

631
00:28:03,227 --> 00:28:03,947
No.

632
00:28:04,747 --> 00:28:06,306
Right now, you're being cowardly.

633
00:28:06,306 --> 00:28:08,467
You're afraid of getting hurt.

634
00:28:08,467 --> 00:28:09,947
So you refuse to love.

635
00:28:10,786 --> 00:28:12,667
You're afraid of carrying
others' expectations.

636
00:28:12,707 --> 00:28:13,306
So you just

637
00:28:13,546 --> 00:28:15,306
never open your heart to anyone.

638
00:28:16,267 --> 00:28:16,947
Am I right?

639
00:28:17,866 --> 00:28:18,546
You're right.

640
00:28:19,987 --> 00:28:20,826
In my heart,

641
00:28:21,187 --> 00:28:22,626
all that love is pointless.

642
00:28:23,626 --> 00:28:25,626
I'd rather spend that time
drafting more reports,

643
00:28:25,626 --> 00:28:26,826
or reading more papers

644
00:28:27,386 --> 00:28:28,747
to secure my spot

645
00:28:28,747 --> 00:28:29,707
and get that offer.

646
00:28:32,306 --> 00:28:33,786
Let's get things straight now.

647
00:28:34,027 --> 00:28:34,907
No more trouble later.

648
00:28:36,427 --> 00:28:36,866
It's good.

649
00:28:40,187 --> 00:28:40,947
What do you mean?

650
00:28:44,066 --> 00:28:45,507
Did I make you feel troubled?

651
00:28:46,987 --> 00:28:48,146
Are you serious?

652
00:28:48,546 --> 00:28:50,786
You want us to have nothing
but rivalry from now on?

653
00:28:54,467 --> 00:28:55,187
I'm serious.

654
00:30:07,786 --> 00:30:08,146
Hello?

655
00:30:10,947 --> 00:30:11,386
Yan Fei?

656
00:30:18,907 --> 00:30:20,947
I'll be right there. Don't panic.

657
00:30:21,866 --> 00:30:22,792
Send me your location.

658
00:30:26,267 --> 00:30:27,346
What's with your brother?

659
00:30:27,907 --> 00:30:29,672
Not answering calls,
nowhere to be found.

660
00:30:30,427 --> 00:30:31,586
If he wants to break up,

661
00:30:32,066 --> 00:30:32,947
he should just say so.

662
00:30:33,106 --> 00:30:34,346
Is it so hard to be blunt?

663
00:30:34,866 --> 00:30:37,507
I don't believe he can hide forever.

664
00:30:37,907 --> 00:30:39,826
So you were actually trying
to ambush my brother?

665
00:30:39,947 --> 00:30:41,586
But since my car was restricted today

666
00:30:41,586 --> 00:30:42,707
and I drove his car instead,

667
00:30:42,786 --> 00:30:44,386
you accidentally ended up cornering me?

668
00:30:45,866 --> 00:30:46,947
We're both women.

669
00:30:47,427 --> 00:30:49,747
I'm sure you understand this situation.

670
00:30:50,306 --> 00:30:52,008
We've been together for over six months.

671
00:30:53,747 --> 00:30:54,106
Look.

672
00:30:55,826 --> 00:30:57,907
This is the photo your brother and I
took abroad.

673
00:30:58,306 --> 00:31:00,586
Everything was fine
when he dropped me at the airport.

674
00:31:01,747 --> 00:31:02,667
It's been days now.

675
00:31:03,227 --> 00:31:04,106
No reply

676
00:31:04,306 --> 00:31:05,066
to texts or calls.

677
00:31:05,427 --> 00:31:06,106
What's the deal?

678
00:31:06,546 --> 00:31:08,346
But I can't reach him either right now.

679
00:31:08,907 --> 00:31:10,626
I just called his assistant.

680
00:31:11,227 --> 00:31:12,947
She said something important came up.

681
00:31:12,987 --> 00:31:13,507
I also think

682
00:31:13,507 --> 00:31:15,507
he's definitely tied up
with something critical.

683
00:31:15,707 --> 00:31:17,187
Maybe just wait a bit longer?

684
00:31:17,586 --> 00:31:18,267
Just excuses.

685
00:31:18,546 --> 00:31:20,707
What could be so urgent
he can't even text back?

686
00:31:22,106 --> 00:31:24,667
I don't care. He owes me an explanation.

687
00:31:25,027 --> 00:31:26,227
I'll break up with him,

688
00:31:26,386 --> 00:31:28,586
but not by being dumped unknowingly.

689
00:31:30,467 --> 00:31:32,866
Do you have specific demands?

690
00:31:33,907 --> 00:31:34,632
Two million.

691
00:31:38,586 --> 00:31:39,346
A hundred thousand.

692
00:31:39,626 --> 00:31:40,346
Not a cent more.

693
00:31:40,826 --> 00:31:42,586
But give him three more days.

694
00:31:42,907 --> 00:31:43,626
When he's back,

695
00:31:43,626 --> 00:31:45,066
you two sort everything out.

696
00:31:45,747 --> 00:31:47,346
Yan Da isn't the person you think he is.

697
00:31:47,546 --> 00:31:49,106
He's my brother. I know him.

698
00:31:49,427 --> 00:31:50,306
He must be swamped

699
00:31:50,306 --> 00:31:51,866
by something important.

700
00:31:52,227 --> 00:31:53,747
As for his work,

701
00:31:53,747 --> 00:31:54,907
I honestly don't know much.

702
00:31:55,187 --> 00:31:56,306
I called his assistant.

703
00:31:56,306 --> 00:31:57,306
She was evasive too.

704
00:31:58,267 --> 00:32:00,427
This hundred thousand is your own money?

705
00:32:00,826 --> 00:32:01,747
I have credit cards,

706
00:32:02,467 --> 00:32:03,626
but little cash on hand.

707
00:32:03,626 --> 00:32:04,826
That's the best I can do.

708
00:32:05,546 --> 00:32:07,027
But after you take the money,

709
00:32:07,106 --> 00:32:08,267
sign an agreement with me.

710
00:32:08,667 --> 00:32:10,386
You must promise not to tell anyone

711
00:32:10,467 --> 00:32:11,786
about your relationship.

712
00:32:12,146 --> 00:32:13,546
Also, those pictures

713
00:32:13,667 --> 00:32:14,346
and chat records.

714
00:32:14,987 --> 00:32:16,826
Everything waits until he comes back.

715
00:32:17,267 --> 00:32:20,507
I won't sign. And I won't
take your money.

716
00:32:21,106 --> 00:32:21,866
But don't worry.

717
00:32:22,427 --> 00:32:24,626
Hearing what you just said,
I agree to three days.

718
00:32:24,626 --> 00:32:25,507
After three days,

719
00:32:25,707 --> 00:32:27,786
if your brother
still vanishes like this,

720
00:32:28,066 --> 00:32:28,586
not even you,

721
00:32:28,907 --> 00:32:29,786
nor ten blood sisters

722
00:32:30,306 --> 00:32:31,027
could save him.

723
00:32:34,227 --> 00:32:35,027
I understand.

724
00:32:35,747 --> 00:32:37,227
But let me say something.

725
00:32:38,346 --> 00:32:40,626
Money can't fix everything.

726
00:32:41,187 --> 00:32:43,507
Sometimes, it just creates
more problems.

727
00:32:48,507 --> 00:32:48,866
But

728
00:32:49,267 --> 00:32:50,146
you're decent.

729
00:32:50,707 --> 00:32:53,386
In my opinion, Yan Da
should call you brother.

730
00:33:07,066 --> 00:33:07,586
What now?

731
00:33:09,306 --> 00:33:09,987
Another round?

732
00:33:10,586 --> 00:33:11,066
Come on.

733
00:33:11,427 --> 00:33:12,586
Two of the same, please.

734
00:33:16,507 --> 00:33:16,907
Thanks.

735
00:33:19,546 --> 00:33:20,947
What? Your brother isn't back yet,

736
00:33:20,947 --> 00:33:22,027
and you're handling this?

737
00:33:23,786 --> 00:33:25,346
I've been dumped like that before.

738
00:33:26,027 --> 00:33:27,907
That's why I get her heartbreak.

739
00:33:28,267 --> 00:33:30,947
Helping her feel better is worth it.

740
00:33:31,467 --> 00:33:32,427
Besides, I think

741
00:33:33,027 --> 00:33:35,027
that girl genuinely cares
about my brother.

742
00:33:35,546 --> 00:33:36,507
Her demanding money

743
00:33:36,507 --> 00:33:37,747
was just to force him out.

744
00:33:38,146 --> 00:33:39,707
She showed me their photos together

745
00:33:40,146 --> 00:33:40,987
and chat records

746
00:33:41,386 --> 00:33:42,467
My brother even kept

747
00:33:42,467 --> 00:33:43,786
liking her posts

748
00:33:43,786 --> 00:33:45,027
from his secret account.

749
00:33:45,106 --> 00:33:46,826
Can't blame her for getting obsessed.

750
00:33:47,187 --> 00:33:48,907
If that's the case, your brother's

751
00:33:50,227 --> 00:33:51,227
totally at fault here.

752
00:33:51,586 --> 00:33:52,346
Exactly.

753
00:33:52,707 --> 00:33:53,747
He's unreasonable.

754
00:33:54,507 --> 00:33:56,546
He won't even break up properly.

755
00:33:56,546 --> 00:33:57,386
Let me tell you.

756
00:33:57,507 --> 00:33:59,187
The scariest thing in dating
is a breakup

757
00:33:59,187 --> 00:34:00,267
with no explanation.

758
00:34:00,546 --> 00:34:01,866
A vanished person

759
00:34:02,027 --> 00:34:04,346
doesn't just ruin your relationship.

760
00:34:04,826 --> 00:34:06,707
He crushes your faith in love

761
00:34:06,786 --> 00:34:07,786
and your self-confidence.

762
00:34:08,387 --> 00:34:09,427
You'll doubt

763
00:34:09,427 --> 00:34:11,066
if you do anything wrong

764
00:34:11,387 --> 00:34:12,987
and fail anything,

765
00:34:13,347 --> 00:34:14,787
or you are

766
00:34:14,827 --> 00:34:15,987
too ugly or fat

767
00:34:16,307 --> 00:34:18,546
to get a proper goodbye?

768
00:34:22,387 --> 00:34:22,987
Just rambling.

769
00:34:24,666 --> 00:34:25,387
Actually,

770
00:34:26,387 --> 00:34:27,947
even clean breakups

771
00:34:29,467 --> 00:34:30,586
may still hurt.

772
00:34:31,387 --> 00:34:32,427
You'll get hurt

773
00:34:32,987 --> 00:34:35,507
if he leaves too ruthlessly.

774
00:34:35,947 --> 00:34:37,827
Get hurt if he moves on too fast.

775
00:34:38,027 --> 00:34:39,947
If he finds someone new quickly,

776
00:34:40,146 --> 00:34:42,507
you hurt more. Being hurt
is unavoidable.

777
00:34:45,987 --> 00:34:47,987
Teachers graded us back in school.

778
00:34:48,947 --> 00:34:49,427
Later,

779
00:34:50,186 --> 00:34:51,987
as interns, mentors graded us.

780
00:34:52,347 --> 00:34:53,947
If we become lawyers in the future,

781
00:34:54,827 --> 00:34:55,947
clients become our graders.

782
00:34:56,467 --> 00:34:57,347
Love has no grades,

783
00:34:57,907 --> 00:34:58,787
no standard answer,

784
00:34:59,307 --> 00:35:00,027
and no standards.

785
00:35:00,546 --> 00:35:01,787
We've memorized endless laws,

786
00:35:01,907 --> 00:35:02,787
but show me one

787
00:35:03,507 --> 00:35:04,467
that dictates

788
00:35:05,027 --> 00:35:06,507
exactly when

789
00:35:06,666 --> 00:35:07,787
the right words

790
00:35:07,907 --> 00:35:09,586
or the perfect action exist?

791
00:35:11,427 --> 00:35:12,226
Impossible.

792
00:35:13,546 --> 00:35:15,907
Statutes only show risks

793
00:35:15,947 --> 00:35:18,467
we might encounter.

794
00:35:19,546 --> 00:35:20,666
I'll bet with you.

795
00:35:20,746 --> 00:35:22,507
Look at our firm's partners,

796
00:35:22,507 --> 00:35:23,507
every one of them,

797
00:35:23,626 --> 00:35:24,787
with mid-levels included.

798
00:35:25,427 --> 00:35:27,546
They may have been artistic when young,

799
00:35:27,666 --> 00:35:29,106
but asking them to pursue a love

800
00:35:29,186 --> 00:35:30,746
without counting the cost now

801
00:35:31,546 --> 00:35:33,106
is nearly impossible.

802
00:35:33,867 --> 00:35:35,186
As long as we work hard enough,

803
00:35:35,266 --> 00:35:36,307
even Earth could wander.

804
00:35:36,307 --> 00:35:37,947
The Trisolarans were even defeated.

805
00:35:38,146 --> 00:35:40,787
But the professional instinct
engraved in their bones

806
00:35:41,027 --> 00:35:41,827
is undefeatable.

807
00:35:41,827 --> 00:35:42,787
Miss Yan, look at you.

808
00:35:43,307 --> 00:35:45,507
How many male lawyers broke your hearts

809
00:35:45,706 --> 00:35:48,106
to make you become this bitter?

810
00:35:49,706 --> 00:35:50,626
You're teasing me?

811
00:35:51,186 --> 00:35:52,507
How about you and Ren Jiatong?

812
00:35:54,987 --> 00:35:55,546
Not great.

813
00:35:57,347 --> 00:35:59,746
Flirting all day at the firm.

814
00:35:59,787 --> 00:36:01,226
Guo Xiaoyu might not notice,

815
00:36:01,307 --> 00:36:03,266
but I see everything clearly!

816
00:36:03,787 --> 00:36:04,706
You think you're smart.

817
00:36:05,266 --> 00:36:07,226
I guess Holmes is a also a bad guy,

818
00:36:07,507 --> 00:36:09,066
moving on to a new girlfriend so fast.

819
00:36:10,226 --> 00:36:11,266
Suit yourself then.

820
00:38:18,186 --> 00:38:20,027
(Ren Jiatong, what are you
so afraid of?)

821
00:38:20,787 --> 00:38:22,907
What can't you face?

822
00:38:23,027 --> 00:38:24,106
Why are you so afraid

823
00:38:24,787 --> 00:38:26,706
to admit your own feelings?

824
00:38:26,706 --> 00:38:27,467
(You act cold.)

825
00:38:27,467 --> 00:38:28,907
(Right now, you're being cowardly.)

826
00:38:28,907 --> 00:38:31,066
You're afraid of getting hurt.

827
00:38:31,066 --> 00:38:32,546
So you refuse to love.

828
00:38:33,387 --> 00:38:35,266
You're afraid of carrying
others' expectations.

829
00:38:35,307 --> 00:38:35,907
so you just

830
00:38:36,146 --> 00:38:37,907
never open your heart to anyone.

831
00:38:40,746 --> 00:38:42,146
(Let's get things straight now.)

832
00:38:42,387 --> 00:38:43,432
(No more trouble later.)

833
00:38:44,827 --> 00:38:45,266
It's fine.

834
00:38:46,146 --> 00:38:46,907
What do you mean?

835
00:38:50,027 --> 00:38:51,467
Did I make you feel troubled?

836
00:39:06,346 --> 00:39:08,712
(Body warmer)

837
00:39:11,848 --> 00:39:13,864
(Body warmer, brown sugar)

838
00:39:14,351 --> 00:39:17,001
(Body warmer and brown sugar
on the table. Note first hotpot date.)

839
00:39:17,001 --> 00:39:17,832
(You may need it recently.)

840
00:39:33,746 --> 00:39:35,027
Post it if you want.

841
00:39:35,467 --> 00:39:36,947
Be proactive when pursuing a girl.

842
00:39:39,427 --> 00:39:40,467
Are you lecturing me now?

843
00:39:46,867 --> 00:39:47,706
What if right now,

844
00:39:48,586 --> 00:39:51,546
that lawyer you set to "only he can see"

845
00:39:51,947 --> 00:39:53,146
came back

846
00:39:53,626 --> 00:39:55,546
and chased you hard, would you

847
00:39:55,987 --> 00:39:56,626
